Future
******

   Quite frankly, I hope this program doesn't have a future :-) I would
like to see a program like this to be included in the distribution of
the operating system, just like the "Prefs/WBPattern" program does.
Since this is currently not the case, feel free to contact me (see
@{"Author Info" Link "Author Info"}) for any suggestions or comments you have concerning this
program.


@EndNode

